column3: I do not mean to be rude, but I prefer to be left undisturbed while on guard duty. Move along, please.
Are you sure you wish to enter with a fixed party?
Are you sure you wish to enter with a matched party?
You intend to enter Heaven–on–High alone? While I have heard tales of your strength from Rasho, I fear that even a warrior of your caliber may be hard-pressed. Will you not reconsider?
Are you sure you wish to enter alone?
From which floor will you enter?
Proceed to the next floor with your current party?
